title: Worst Date Wednesday: Kevin & Mandy's Day of Fun & Enchantment
description: "Mandy" tells us about an insane date she went on that started with the guy having to stop at a family gathering to help settle an argument.  Then he sent her to a bar for 5 hours without him, WHILE he tried to help settle the argument.  It doesn't end well but AFTER the date Mandy found out something even more extreme that he was telling his family about their relationship, reminder, this is the first date....
